<li sourcefile="finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/review-collections-information.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70">Select the <strong sourcefile="finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/review-collections-information.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70">Collections</strong> tab.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/review-collections-information.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Expand or collapse the <strong sourcefile="finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/review-collections-information.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Collections defaults</strong> section.</li>
